<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email Address</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c5aa0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            color: #2c5aa0;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .verification-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c5aa0, #17a2b8);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .verification-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .verification-code {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 2px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }
        .code-display {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        .actions {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            margin: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .button-primary {
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
        }
        .button-secondary {
            background-color: #6c757d;
            color: white;
        }
        .important-info {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .security-info {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .steps {
            background-color: #e8f4fd;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #2c5aa0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .step-item {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .step-number {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            background-color: #2c5aa0;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">HealthCare Platform</div>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="title">üìß Verify Your Email Address</h1>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= patientName %>,</p>
            
            <p>Welcome to our healthcare platform! To complete your registration and ensure the security of your account, please verify your email address.</p>
            
            <div class="verification-card">
                <div class="verification-icon">üîê</div>
                <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 20px;">Email Verification Required</h3>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0;">Use the verification code below to activate your account</p>
                
                <div class="verification-code">
                    <div>Your Verification Code:</div>
                    <div class="code-display"><%= verificationCode %></div>
                    <div style="font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9;">This code expires in <%= expiryTime %> minutes</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="steps">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #2c5aa0;">How to Verify Your Email</h3>
                <div class="step-item">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    Click the "Verify Email" button below or return to the registration page
                </div>
                <div class="step-item">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    Enter the 6-digit verification code: <strong><%= verificationCode %></strong>
                </div>
                <div class="step-item">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    Complete your profile setup and start using the platform
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="actions">
                <% if (verificationUrl) { %>
                    <a href="<%= verificationUrl %>" class="button button-primary">Verify Email Address</a>
                <% } %>
                <% if (resendUrl) { %>
                    <a href="<%= resendUrl %>" class="button button-secondary">Resend Code</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
            
            <div class="important-info">
                <strong>Important:</strong><br>
                ‚Ä¢ This verification code will expire in <%= expiryTime %> minutes<br>
                ‚Ä¢ You can request a new code if this one expires<br>
                ‚Ä¢ Keep this code confidential and do not share it with anyone<br>
                ‚Ä¢ If you didn't create this account, please ignore this email
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-info">
                <strong>Security Notice:</strong><br>
                For your protection, never share your verification code with anyone. Our support team will never ask for your verification code via email or phone. If you receive suspicious communications, please report them to our security team immediately.
            </div>
            
            <p>Once your email is verified, you'll be able to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Book appointments with qualified doctors</li>
                <li>Access your medical records and history</li>
                <li>Receive appointment reminders and notifications</li>
                <li>Manage your profile and preferences</li>
                <li>Connect with healthcare professionals securely</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>If you're having trouble with verification or didn't request this account, please contact our support team for assistance.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for choosing our healthcare platform. We're excited to help you on your health journey!</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            The Healthcare Platform Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This verification code was sent to: <%= patientEmail %></p>
            <p>Need help? Contact us at support@healthcareplatform.com or call (555) 123-4567</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Healthcare Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>